Telkom has announced its Big Deal promotion for January 2018. The promotion is a 24-month contract priced at R599 per month, which includes: The free LIT_TV Vox and Wi-Fi range extender are available for the first 5,000 customers. New Telkom broadband clients will qualify for a free Wi-Fi ADSL router and installation when signing up for the 24-month contract. The deal is available until 31 January 2018. Terms and conditions are available on Telkom’s website. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>